modules.description: This module defines a comprehensive set of icon constants representing UI elements and actions, along with functions to convert them to S-expressions, retrieve frame data, generate SVG nodes with customizable attributes, and access their string names. It works primarily with the enumerated type `t` listing each icon variant, alongside standard OCaml lists and sexp types. Concrete use cases include rendering icons in a web-based code editor interface using virtual DOM, serializing icon states for configuration or debugging, and mapping icon names to visual elements in a theme-aware UI.
